## Streak Milestone Celebrations

| Milestone | Celebration | Badge |
|-----------|------------|-------|
| 3 days | Inline "Nice start!" toast + haptic | 🌱 Sprout |
| 7 days | Confetti animation + "One week!" banner | 🌿 Seedling |
| 14 days | Confetti + "Two weeks strong!" | 🌳 Sapling |
| 30 days | Full-screen celebration + share card | 🔥 On Fire |
| 60 days | Full-screen + unique badge | ⭐ Star |
| 100 days | Full-screen + golden badge + share card | 🏆 Champion |
| 365 days | Full-screen + annual recap animation | 💎 Diamond |
| 500 days | Full-screen + platinum badge | 🌟 Legend |
| 1000 days | Full-screen + custom animation | 👑 Immortal |

**Celebration message variants (2-3 per tier for variable reward):**
- 3 days: "Nice start!" / "Three days in! You're building something." / "Day 3 — the hardest part is behind you."
- 7 days: "One week!" / "7 days strong! Consistency is your superpower." / "A whole week of showing up!"
- 14 days: "Two weeks strong!" / "14 days — this is becoming a real habit." / "Two weeks of you at your best."
- 30 days: "Unstoppable!" / "30 days. You've proven something to yourself." / "A whole month. That's commitment."
- 60 days: "Two months of consistency!" / "60 days. That's not luck — that's discipline." / "Two months down. You're building something real."
- 100 days: "Triple digits!" / "100 days. Most people don't make it to 10." / "One hundred days of showing up. That's a lifestyle."
- 365 days: "A full year!" / "365 days. You really did it." / "One year of {habit}. Take a moment — you've earned it."
- 500 days: "Legend status!" / "500 days. That's not a streak — that's who you are." / "Five hundred days. Words aren't enough."
- 1000 days: "Immortal." / "1,000 days. You've transcended streaks." / "A thousand days of showing up for yourself."
- Selection: rotate by `habit.id.hashValue % variantCount` so each habit gets a consistent but different variant.

**Streak loss compassion (2-3 variants, rotate by habit.id.hashValue):**
- "{old streak} days is {old streak} more than zero. Ready for the next one?"
- "That {old streak}-day streak built real discipline. Start the next chapter."
- "{old streak} days of effort don't vanish — they're in your stats forever."
- Delivery: warm inline card in habit row (not toast — toasts feel dismissive for this moment). Haptic `.light` (not `.warning`). Shows on first view after streak breaks.
- NEVER show: "You lost your streak!" or any punitive language.

**Celebration priority queue (when multiple events fire simultaneously):**
1. Undo toast is suppressed during all-complete celebration (confetti takes priority)
2. Confetti plays first (2 seconds)
3. Streak milestone toast queues after confetti completes
4. Badge unlock ceremony modal queues after milestone toast dismisses
5. Share card prompt appears inside the badge ceremony modal (not separately)
Never stack more than one overlay simultaneously. Use a serial queue with completion handlers.

**Share cards (v1.0 — NOT deferred, this is the only viral loop):** At milestones 7/30/100/365, show "Share your streak!" button. Image card rendered via `ImageRenderer` ONLY when user taps Share (lazy, not eager — avoids main-thread contention during celebration): "I just hit a {N}-day streak on {habit} with DailyArc!" with app branding and App Store link. **CRITICAL for growth:** without this, the app launches with zero viral mechanics. Share via standard `ShareLink`. **Privacy guard:** Do NOT include habit name in share card if it could disclose health data (e.g., "Take Medication"). Use generic "a daily habit" for sensitive-sounding habit names.

